# audience-data-models

## Core Data Models

### Fan Profile Structure
- Unified music identity system linking profiles across platforms
- Genre affinity scoring (0-100) based on listening patterns
- Artist type categorization with weighted relationships
- Platform-specific engagement metrics aggregation
- Behavioral trait mapping from music consumption patterns

### Segmentation Rules
- Multi-criteria segmentation engine supporting:
  - Genre preferences (primary/secondary)
  - Artist affinity scores
  - Platform engagement levels
  - Content interaction patterns
- Dynamic segment size estimation
- Real-time audience qualification rules

### Engagement Scoring
- Platform-specific scoring algorithms:
  - Spotify: Playlist creation/curation weight
  - YouTube: Artist channel engagement metrics
  - Instagram: Music-related content interaction
- Cross-platform activity correlation
- Temporal engagement patterns
- Genre-based engagement multipliers

### Discovery Models
Located in: `backend/src/services/discovery/discovery.service.ts`
- Music taste matching algorithm (0-100 score)
- Genre correlation mapping
- Artist relationship graphs
- Playlist contribution analysis
- Fan similarity clustering

### Profile Enrichment
Located in: `backend/src/services/spotify/enrichment.service.ts`
- Automated taste profile generation
- Cross-platform identity resolution
- Genre normalization rules
- Artist affinity calculations
- Platform-specific metadata aggregation

## Key Integration Points

### Platform Data Models
- Spotify: User preferences, playlist behavior
- YouTube: Music video engagement
- Instagram: Artist content interaction
- LastFM: Historical listening patterns
- TikTok: Music-related content creation

### Audience Capture
Located in: `backend/src/models/audience-contact.ts`
- Multi-channel consent tracking
- Platform-specific permissions
- Communication preference management
- Source attribution modeling

## Scoring Algorithms

### Match Score Calculation
- Genre weight: 40%
- Artist overlap: 35%
- Platform engagement: 15%
- Content interaction: 10%

### Segment Quality Scoring
- Engagement depth
- Cross-platform presence
- Genre consistency
- Artist affinity strength

